%% RAG Pipeline for Baseball Video Analysis
%%
%% User Query --> Retriever (Vector DB: Features, Annotations, YOLO Outputs)
%% Retriever --> Top-K Relevant Data (Frames, Features, CSV Rows)
%% Top-K Relevant Data --> Generator (LLM: GPT-4, etc.)
%% Generator --> Generated Answer / Explanation
%% Generated Answer / Explanation --> User Interface (CLI, Web, Notebook)
%%
%% Data Sources:
%%   - Mechanical Features CSVs
%%   - Ball Features CSVs
%%   - YOLO Detected Objects
%%   - Annotated Frames
%%
%% Data Sources --> Retriever

graph TD
    A[User Query] --> B[Retriever - Vector DB: Features / Annotations / YOLO Outputs]
    B --> C[Top-K Relevant Data - Frames / Features / CSV Rows]
    C --> D[Generator - LLM: GPT-4 etc.]
    D --> E[Generated Answer / Explanation]
    E --> F[User Interface - CLI / Web / Notebook]
    subgraph Data Sources
        G1[Mechanical Features CSVs]
        G2[Ball Features CSVs]
        G3[YOLO Detected Objects]
        G4[Annotated Frames]
    end
    G1 --> B
    G2 --> B
    G3 --> B
    G4 --> B
